stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> ServerSelect: outer loop esi=0..10
    ServerSelect --> ConnectAttempt: pick IP from<br/>40-entry table
    ConnectAttempt --> Connected: TCP 443 succeeds
    ConnectAttempt --> Sleep: connect fails
    Sleep --> ConnectAttempt: GetTickCount-driven<br/>60s wait (cfg word [0x413e50])
    ConnectAttempt --> Aborted: counter ≥ 5<br/>(cfg word [0x413e5c])
    Aborted --> ServerSelect: rotate to next IP
    Connected --> CommandLoop
    CommandLoop --> ExecuteCmd: dispatch by opcode
    ExecuteCmd --> ShellExec: opcode = exec
    ExecuteCmd --> DriveEnum: opcode = enum_drives
    ExecuteCmd --> FileOps: opcode = file_op
    ExecuteCmd --> ProcEnum: opcode = enum_procs
    ShellExec --> CommandLoop: send output back
    DriveEnum --> CommandLoop
    FileOps --> CommandLoop
    ProcEnum --> CommandLoop
    CommandLoop --> Connected: server keep-alive
    CommandLoop --> Sleep: server disconnect
    Connected --> Done: special opcode 0xfffff
    Done --> [*]: print "------End------!"
